{"tid":824852,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"沙咀懲教所職員營房塌毀　室內情況一覽無遺","createTime":"2018-09-17T09:01:40.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-17T09:01:40.000Z","uid":127121,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"79214a252ee355e5d367f925cbfcc6e2bb36534f","tid":824852,"uid":127121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-17T09:01:40.000Z","msg":"颱風「山竹」吹襲之處受到廣泛破壞，大嶼山沙咀懲教所初級職員營房亦不能幸免。有懲教人員透露，十間營房中，有一間營房損毀嚴重，從片段所見，營房大幅外牆倒塌，致室內情況一覽無遺，家具亦東歪西倒，甚至吹到路邊，其餘營房的門囗地台全部陷落，整條行人路盡毀，現場只見一片頹垣敗瓦。<br />\n<br />\n本報已向懲教署查詢，正待回覆。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/1189395391192326/videos/2012917838998715/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F1189395391192326%2Fvideos%2F2012917838998715%2F&d=zY%2FQSSMQZOo%2Fp9VqewScKjQ9OVC7k%2FvddpU5ARN7O10%3D&h=251546ca\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/1189395391192326/videos/2012917838998715/</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.am730.com.hk/news/%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/%E6%B2%99%E5%92%80%E6%87%B2%E6%95%99%E6%89%80%E8%81%B7%E5%93%A1%E7%87%9F%E6%88%BF%E5%A1%8C%E6%AF%80%E3%80%80%E5%AE%A4%E5%85%A7%E6%83%85%E6%B3%81%E4%B8%80%E8%A6%BD%E7%84%A1%E9%81%BA-142319\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.am730.com.hk%2Fnews%2F%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2581%259E%2F%25E6%25B2%2599%25E5%2592%2580%25E6%2587%25B2%25E6%2595%2599%25E6%2589%2580%25E8%2581%25B7%25E5%2593%25A1%25E7%2587%259F%25E6%2588%25BF%25E5%25A1%258C%25E6%25AF%2580%25E3%2580%2580%25E5%25AE%25A4%25E5%2585%25A7%25E6%2583%2585%25E6%25B3%2581%25E4%25B8%2580%25E8%25A6%25BD%25E7%2584%25A1%25E9%2581%25BA-142319&d=zY%2FQSSMQZOo%2Fp9VqewScKjQ9OVC7k%2FvddpU5ARN7O10%3D&h=351a8c46\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.am730.com.hk/news/%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/%E6%B2%99%E5%92%80%E6%87%B2%E6%95%99%E6%89%80%E8%81%B7%E5%93%A1%E7%87%9F%E6%88%BF%E5%A1%8C%E6%AF%80%E3%80%80%E5%AE%A4%E5%85%A7%E6%83%85%E6%B3%81%E4%B8%80%E8%A6%BD%E7%84%A1%E9%81%BA-142319</a>"}]}